::Striker::

Striker flies toward Savanna's position, scanning the ground for any sign of 
danger. Suddenly a plasma shot flies at him, Striker barely avoiding it in 
time.

He growls, flying down toward the forest. Spotting a bot, he pulls out his 
rifle, firing a shot at it.
